<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THIH AH THIH HNAWH PHU</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thih ah thih hnawhphu, nun ah nun hnawhphu
 Chim le phuan dingmi, Thawngthabia ka ngei
 Jesuh khrih dawtnak kong,
 Ka hmur le ka in a tlinhlo caah,
 Lungduh in dawtnak kong ka chim kholo, Cu caah ka tap tawn.

[C1]
   Maw ka Bawi Jesuh, na dawtnak kong hi
   Ka hmur le ka nih, a tlinhlo zongah, Nifa ka nun zia in
   Na ca tehteh tha, ka si zungzal lai
   Na zulcia keneh dawh cu ka zul lai, Dinnak ram phak hlan tiang.

[V2]
 Minung fimnak nih, minung a thleng lo
 Minung thiamnak nih, mi a sersiam lo, Pathian thlarau asi,
 Pentikos ni ah, Mi thawngthum thleng tu
 Piter chim mi bia, thluachuah a petu, Pathian thlarau a si.

[V3]
 Joshua le a ral, kap nih ral an do
 Mosses le Aron, Hur inih thla an cam, Cu caah ral an tei
 Sehtan raldo in, ka kal lio ah hin
 Thlarau fa le nih, ka ca thla an cam, Cu ca'h ka hna a ngam.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
</song>